'''Oleksiy Kostusyev''' ({{lang-uk|<U+041E><U+043B><U+0435><U+043A><U+0441><U+0456><U+0439> <U+041E><U+043B><U+0435><U+043A><U+0441><U+0456><U+0439><U+043E><U+0432><U+0438><U+0447> <U+041A><U+043E><U+0441><U+0442><U+0443><U+0441><U+0454><U+0432>}}; June 29, 1954) is a Ukrainian politician and former mayor of [[Odessa]].


